<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Clamber" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Clamber,</orth> to climb: <cit><quote>c. not you up to the casements then,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.5.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 5, 31</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ing the walls to eye him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.226" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 226</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>on the pendent boughs her coronet weeds --ing to hang,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.174" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 174</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>